extends(src='layout.sgr')
  block(name='content')
    h2 Software Engineer &amp; Consultant
    p I evangelize a document, test, code and iterate workflow to create robust and maintainable software.
    //-block(name='banner')
      //-h1.banner Software Engineer & Consultant
    h3 Document
    pi(md) Developers can encourage a document-first approach to writing maintainable software.
    pi(md) Tools: [swagger](http://swagger.io/), [cucumber](https://cucumber.io/), [mkcli](https://github.com/mkdoc/mkcli)
    h3 Test
    p Testing software is an integral part of the process, as a software developer we can leverage test frameworks, code coverage and continuous integration to develop robust programs.

    pi(md) Tools: [ava](https://github.com/avajs/ava), [mocha](http://mochajs.org/), [chai](http://chaijs.com/), [istanbul](https://github.com/gotwarlost/istanbul)
    h3 Code
    p Developers should optimize their environment and respect the DRY principle in order to increase efficiency.
